Yeah.
Look, I'll make it official.

00:09:38,885 --> 00:09:40,386
I'll go in with her,
same deal.

00:09:40,386 --> 00:09:42,822
We'll go 50/50,
exactly the terms detailed.

00:09:42,822 --> 00:09:44,857
